{"type": "article", "id": 18432, "title": "Koppel 腕表", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-03T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 141, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122409YVXpNbTWuPcl0dQL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这一系列腕表的原型来自 Georg Jensen（乔治·杰生）在 1977 年发布的经典款 The Koppel，有非常清晰的白色表盘、纤细的指针和圆点刻度。新系列将现代技术融入其中，同时保留原本的干净简约。一共三种样式，带年历、带动力储备显示或带手上链小三针，搭配皮质表带，有古典感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122408Vbdn1HIatCPWE0s4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41741742\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122408m4a1YP7kn5fZvyVe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37609329\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122409cP1Qfubg6hFX4E3M.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37609329\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}